<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="534" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,1194,2011]" pageId="6" pageNumber="534">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1914,1939]" pageId="6" pageNumber="534">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species can be distinguished by the vertex lacking a submarginal brown stripe between the eyes, the very short connective and the preatrial processes of the aedeagus tapering to a slightly broadened foot– shaped apex.
</paragraph>
